or vehicle systems","identifier":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC23-10150-Optimize-CarPlay-for-vehicle-systems","kind":"article","abstract":[{"text":"Discover how you can integrate CarPlay into modern vehicle systems. We’ll show you how to adjust CarPlay for any high-resolution display — regardless of configuration or size. Learn how you can use CarPlay-supplied metadata and video streams to show information on additional displays, and find out how advances in wireless connectivity, audio, and video encoding can help prepare your vehicle system for the next generation of CarPlay.","type":"text"}],"type":"topic","role":"sampleCode"},"doc://WWDCNotes/documentation/WWDCNotes/WWDC16-722-Developing-CarPlay-Systems-Part-1":{"url":"\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc16-722-developing-carplay-systems-part-1","title":"Developing CarPlay Systems, Part 1","identifier":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC16-722-Developing-CarPlay-Systems-Part-1","role":"sampleCode","kind":"article","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"CarPlay is a smarter, safer way to use your iPhone in the car. Learn how CarPlay works and how to design your car’s infotainment system to work seamlessly with iPhone. Understand best practices for a great user experience that integrates CarPlay with the car’s native system."}],"type":"topic"},"https://developer.apple.com/wwdc19/252":{"type":"download","url":"https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/wwdc19\/252","identifier":"https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/wwdc19\/252","checksum":null},"doc://WWDCNotes/documentation/WWDCNotes/WWDC17-717-Developing-Wireless-CarPlay-Systems":{"kind":"article","url":"\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc17-717-developing-wireless-carplay-systems","title":"Developing Wireless CarPlay Systems","role":"sampleCode","type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"Wireless CarPlay is perfect for any trip. Get in your car without taking your iPhone out of your bag or pocket, and start experiencing CarPlay effortlessly. Learn how to design y